                    Booking Made <span class="text-primary-600">Simpler</span> Than Ever
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4">
                    We've streamlined every step to ensure you get the best service with zero friction.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block pb-2">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-primary-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
                    <span>Follow the Path</span>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long ml-2"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 relative">
            <!-- Connecting Line (Desktop) -->
            <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[10%] right-[10%] h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200 to-transparent z-0"></div>

            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="relative z-10 group">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-soft rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl text-primary-600 mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-primary-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-slate-200 text-xl pointer-events-none">01</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mb-4">Discover Services</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                    Browse through hundreds of verified categories and find the perfect match for your specific needs.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="relative z-10 group">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-soft rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center text-3xl text-indigo-600 mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-indigo-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar-check"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-slate-200 text-xl pointer-events-none">02</div>
